Second Department,

February, 1978

(February 22, 1978)* The People of the State of New York ex rel. Lee Higgs, Petitioner, v Superintendent Arthur Kill Correctional Facility et al., Respondents.*1146

Not published with other decisions of February, 1978, 61 AD2d 782. [Rep.

Application by petitioner for a writ of habeas corpus, denied, without costs. Hopkins, J. P., Latham, Damiani and Titone, JJ., concur.
